{"tid":209482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"董建華身體不適　瑪麗急症室求診","createTime":"2017-04-20T08:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T13:55:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":186,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb111c5239d94818e54931895b8af382b81f577","tid":209482,"uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/bkn-20170420164744438-0420_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170420%2Fbkn-20170420164744438-0420_00822_001.html&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f84fb6ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/bkn-20170420164744438-0420_00822_001.html</a><br />\n前特首董建華疑身體不適入院求診。有市民目擊指，今午約3時10分見到董建華於瑪麗醫院急症室求醫，他當時躺在病床上，閉上雙目，旁邊有約10名疑似G4成員及醫護人員陪同。該市民又指，董建華的太太趙洪娉亦在場，董太眼濕濕，需要人從旁攙扶。<br />\n<br />\n另外，被裁定公職人員行為失當罪成、判監20個月的前特首曾蔭權爵士，目前仍在瑪麗醫院羈留病房留醫。"},{"pid":"5194323c02ba9065dac4b26c1bb8ef186682db13","tid":209482,"uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"趁地淋啦"},{"pid":"8728abc465823787e6f363b63c39d59d5231a24e","tid":209482,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb701bc7fa765cdc8aeae9811be62644902a7d9","tid":209482,"uid":56698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"東方真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都關貪曾事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194378c02673709bbb097c7d464579bed1d4be31","tid":209482,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"有私家醫院唔去?"},{"pid":"ededbf0f2e45fba44ccb1f50f903f6488f9eddfb","tid":209482,"uid":42119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:59:52.00